# 200524 Arty Stable Draconian `.gitignore` File Configurations

## **IGNORE** All Files Or Directories Listed Immediately Below

### **Files to ignore:**

# The below line is responsible for enforcing that files/directories are untracked by default.
*

# The below line enables for directories to be tracked.
!*/

### **Directories to ignore:**

### The above wildcard ("*") pattern applies the default ignore rule to files and directories alike.

#---

## **TRACK** All Files Or Directories Listed Immediately Below

### An Alternative way to look at this is: Do **NOT** Ignore (i.e. TRACK!) Files Or Directories Listed Immediately Below

### **Files to track:**

# The below line is for guidance only. Remove as desired.
#!tracked-file-example.env

# !.gitignore
# !index.html
# !README.md
# !script.js
# !style.css

### **Directories to track:**

### This below lines are for guidance only. Remove as desired.
### Track this directory alone.
!tracked-directory-example/
### Track files within relevant directory.
!tracked-directory-example/**

### Track files within relevant directory.
!blog/*
### track all the files within this (`blog`) directory.
### Track all the files within this (`blog`) directory.
!blog/**

!css/*
!css/**
!js/*
!js/**
!page/*
!page/**
!pic/*
!pic/**
!tool/*
!tool/**

